  <data name="textBox1.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>GDA 6 is a game that focuses on Discrete Mathematics.
It encourages problem solving, analyzing and critical thinking-skills.
In this game, you explore a school that has questions and hints littered
althroughout. You need to answer the questions correctly to unlock
other rooms that will eventually lead you to the final exam.
Passing the final exam ends the game and lets you leave the school.

Remember that you need to score at least 70% to progress through the game.
</value>
